PrecisAppointment of JACQUES BOUCHARD of Blainville, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Parole Board of Canada, Quebec Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective June 28, 2015; and designation to be Vice-Chairperson of the Quebec Regional Division of the Parole Board of Canada, effective immediately.
